=Write a professional payment follow-up message from Michael Craig at Exsto Cura Consilium.

INVOICE DETAILS:
- Client: {{ $json.client_name }}
- Invoice #: {{ $json.invoice_number }}
- Amount: ${{ $json.amount }}
- Days Outstanding: {{ $json.days_outstanding }}
- Status: {{ $json.status }}

Tone guidance by status:
- FOLLOW_UP (7-14 days): Friendly, light touch, assume oversight
- OVERDUE (14-30 days): Professional, clear, note the due date
- ESCALATE (30+ days): Firm, professional, reference contract terms

Write ONLY the email body. No subject line. 3-5 sentences maximum. Do not be aggressive. Maintain the professional senior consultant relationship. Sign off as Michael Craig, Exsto Cura Consilium.
